Build Prerequisites
===================

- [`cmake`](https://cmake.org/) (ver >= 3.2)
- [`conan`](https://conan.io/) (ver >= 1.0)
    - Note the `conan` configuration caveat [described here](https://docs.conan.io/en/latest/howtos/manage_gcc_abi.html).
    - For quickstart, try:

        `conan profile update settings.compiler.libcxx=libstdc++11 default`

Build
=====

- `mkdir build && cd build`
- `conan install ..`
- `cmake .. -G "Unix Makefiles" -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release`
- `cmake --build .`
